					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>Records a gift of land by four persons for providing musical instruments to the god Tirusōmīśvarattu āḻvār at Tirukkuḍamūkkil, a <hi rend="italic">dēvadānam</hi> in Pāmbūr-nāḍu. It is laid down that these musical instruments were to be played on special occasions and the <hi rend="italic">mūlaparuḍaiyār</hi> agreed to carry out this charity. </p>						

						</summary>
